      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, thread the paneer and red pepper onto the skewers (see picture)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> the kebabs with generously all over with salt&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
